"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2000_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2000_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On social media, Richardson posted a photo of his silver and bronze medals side-by-side with the caption: \\\"Trying to collect them all\\\", noting he still had the keirin to go.\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1447, \"end\": 1457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9999102688800298, \"rank\": 8.973773760065838e-05, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the men's canoeing K-2 500m final, Australians Tom Green and Jean van der Westhuyzen finished with a bronze medal.\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1722, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1655, \"end\": 1664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Green\", \"score\": 0.9999999999834017, \"rank\": 1.6630122143180616e-11, \"text\": \"Tom Green\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Green\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Green\"}, {\"begin\": 1669, \"end\": 1692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean_van_der_Westhuyzen\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jean van der Westhuyzen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean_van_der_Westhuyzen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean_van_der_Westhuyzen\"}, {\"begin\": 1669, \"end\": 1692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean_van_der_Westhuyzen\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jean van der Westhuyzen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean_van_der_Westhuyzen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean_van_der_Westhuyzen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Winning an Olympic medal is so special.\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1764, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are so stoked with that,\\\" van der Westhuyzen said.\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1818, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Elsewhere in Paris, the Opals hopes of playing for the gold medal were dashed after a 85-64 loss to the United States in the women's basketball semi-final.\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1975, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1833, \"end\": 1838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999986828243, \"rank\": 1.3170879053537592e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1844, \"end\": 1849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4240213741738963e-20, \"text\": \"Opals\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1924, \"end\": 1937, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999979631261621, \"rank\": 2.002150386475118e-06, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We had to play a perfect game today.\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 2014, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We came out really flat.\", \"from\": 2015, \"to\": 2039, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We had too many turnovers and shot selection wasn't great,\\\" coach Sandy Brondello said.\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2127, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2106, \"end\": 21